On middle, Rahane turns it to the on side and rotates the strike.

FOUR! Lovely shot! Not an easy shot to play but Mayank plays this really well. Short around off, Agarwal waits for it and then late cuts it through third man. The fielder from the deep tries to clean it up but gets beaten to the fence. That boundary also brings up the 100-run stand between the two. This has been a superb partnership from this duo.
Good length ball on off, Rahane punches it through covers and gets a couple as the fielder from sweeper cover cleans it. Gets to 49.
Good length ball on off, Rahane defends it off the back foot.

Fifty for Rahane. Ajinkya Rahane has been amongst the runs recently and he has once again played a classy knock here. Full on middle and off, Rahane flicks it through mid-wicket for a single to get to his 21st Test fifty.
On the fourth stump line, Mayank leaves it.
On the stumps, Agarwal defends it off the front foot.
Slightly shorter, Mayank pulls it to deep mid-wicket and keeps the strike.
Floated on off, Rahane pushes it to cover.
Overpitched on off, Rahane defends it. They are overpitching it to get Rahane to drive.
On off, Rahane flicks it to mid on.
Tossed up on off, Rahane flicks it to the right of mid on and gets a single.
Flighted on off, Mayank finds Mushfiqur at mid on with his glances.
FOUR! Mayank is such a lovely player of spin bowling. Taijul drags it down, Mayank is quick to get on his back foot and pulls it over mid-wicket for a boundary. Good end to the over.
Fuller and on middle, this is driven towards mid on.
Shorter and outside off, this is guided through point for one.
Flighted outside off, Agarwal leaves it alone.
Shorter on off, Mayank plays it through point and gets a couple.
Good shot but just a single. Back of a length on off, Agarwal pulls it with authority but there is a man at deep mid-wicket for a single.
Another short ball, Rahane pulls it behind square on the leg side and gets a single.
On middle, this is worked towards mid-wicket.

FOUR! Swept and swept hard! This is flatter and on the pads, Agarwal decides late to sweep it. He though connects brilliantly and it goes for a boundary in the square leg region.
On middle, Mayank goes back and works it to square leg.
On off, Agarwal hits it down to long on and a single is taken.

FOUR! Up and over! Takes a few steps down the track, converts it into a full toss and lofts it over the mid on fielder and bags another boundary. 250 up for India.
On the stumps, Agarwal stays in the crease this time and keeps it out.
Floated on middle, Rahane defends it off the front foot.
Flighted on the stumps, Ajinkya blocks it.
Shorter on off, Rahane gets on his back foot and punches it to cover.
Floated on off, Rahane comes down the track and slashes it towards long on for a single.
FOUR! India changing gears here. Short on middle, Mayank gets on his back foot, uses the depth of the crease really well and pulls it through square leg for a boundary.

SIX! One of the most toughest shot in the game to play and Mayank plays it with absolute ease. Flighted on off, Mayank comes down the track and goes inside out over extra cover for a maximum.

SIX! That was six the moment it left the bat! Brings up the 150-run stand between the duo. Tossed up on middle and off, Agarwal comes down the track and smashes it with sweetness over the long on fence for a biggie.
Floated on off, Agarwal pushes it to mid on.
Around the pads, MA whips it but finds mid-wicket.
FOUR! This is some absolute masterclass batting against spin. Slightly overpitched on off, Rahane strokes it through mid on and gets a boundary.
Now milks this one to long off for one.

FOUR! 150 up for Mayank. This is superb batting! Shorter on  off, Mayank gets on his back foot and pulls it over cow corner to get to his milestone. He is looking unbeatable at the moment. Subdued celebration from the Karnataka boy. His teammates applaud this gem of a knock. He gives a thumbs up to the dressing room and gets back to his work.

No Ball! Not an ideal start with the new ball as Jayed oversteps. Full and outside off, Rahane strokes it wide of sweeper cover for two.

FOUR! The ball races to the fence in a flash. Rahane moves into the 80s and India go past 300 taking their lead over 150. Good length ball outside off, Rahane slashes it through point for a boundary.

Outside off, Rahane wants to go to Tea unbeaten so he won't even bother playing this. He leaves this one as Australia's Steven Smith.

Ebadot starts with a good length ball way outside off, Agarwal leaves the ball alone.

Full delivery on middle, Mayank looks to defend it but it goes off the inside edge of the bat towards square leg. Mayank wants the second and takes off. Taijul has a shy at the keeper's end but misses. Had he hit, it would have been close.
Good length delivery on off, Agarwal defends it onto the pitch.
Another one on a length around off, Mayank opens the face of the bat and guides it to the slip cordon. 2 runs have come off the over.
Full delivery outside off, Rahane shoulders arms to this one.

FOUR! Poor bowling this from Abu Jayed! He bowls a full delivery on the pads, Rahane will not miss out on these and he just flicks it towards fine leg. Ebadot runs across from deep square leg and puts in a dive to stop it but fails to do so. The ball rolls into the fence.
Good length ball on off, Rahane defends it off the front foot.

OUT! CAUGHT! Finally the partnership is broken and another wicket falls to Abu Jayed. Short of a length outside off, Rahane cuts it uppishly but does not time it well. Unluckily finds Taijul at deep point. Ajinkya unfortunately misses out on a well deserved 100. Has the wicket come too late for Bangladesh though?
Full delivery outside off, Jadeja lets the ball go to the keeper.
Another fullish delivery way outside off, Ravindra shoulders arms to this one.
Good length ball outside off, Mayank shoulders arms to this one.
Fullish delivery on middle, Agarwal looks to defend it but it hits the inside edge of the bat and onto the pads. No harm done though.
Another full delivery outside off, Agarwal drives this to cover.
FOUR! Hammered! Hossain dishes out a full ball outside off, Mayank lunges and thrashes the ball through the cover region for a boundary.
Short ball outside off, Mayank pushes this towards cover and calls Jadeja for a couple. The fielder comes across and cleans it up before it reaches the ropes.
Bouncer! Hossain bowls it on the leg stump, Mayank ducks under it.
Full delivery outside the off stump line, Jadeja lets the ball go to the keeper.
Outside off, left alone by Jadeja.
Full delivery on off, Jadeja gets off the mark by driving this towards mid off.
Good length ball on middle, MA defends it back to the bowler.
Back of a length ball outside off, Mayank punches this off the back foot to cover and crosses over for a single.
Jayed dishes out a full ball outside off, Ravindra does not fiddle with it and lets the ball go to the keeper.
Short of a length ball on middle, Agarwal stands tall and pushes it back to the bowler.
Full delivery this time from Hossain, Agarwal drives it beautifully but it hits the boot of Ebadot and the ball rolls to mid off.
Good length ball outside off, Mayank guides this to third man and takes a single.
EDGED AND FOUR! Good length ball on off, Jadeja attempts to defend but it goes off the outside edge through gully for a boundary.
Full delivery on the pads, Jadeja flicks it to backward square leg and takes a single.
FOUR! That is audacious from Agarwal. He stands tall to this short of a length ball outside off and hammers this over cover and picks up another boundary.
Good length ball on middle, Jadeja works it to mid-wicket.
Fullish delivery on off, Jadeja drives it to mid off.
Another full delivery on off, Jadeja defends it to cover.
Outside off, left alone by Jadeja.
Fullish delivery outside off, Jadeja has no problems in leaving this alone.
Good length ball outside off, Jadeja shoulders arms to this one.
Tosses this one up on off, Mayank plays it back to the bowler.
Floated ball on middle, Agarwal defends it to the leg side.
Loopy ball on middle, Mayank flicks it to square leg.
Fullish delivery on middle, Agarwal pushes this through mid on and takes a single.
Floated ball on off, Jadeja prods forward and defends it to cover.
Full delivery on off, Jadeja pushes it to mid off.
On a length on off, Agarwal pushes it to cover for nothing.
Back of a length delivery on off, Agarwal defends it to mid off of the back foot.
Bowls a full delivery on middle, Agarwal plays it back to the bowler.
Another full one on middle, Agarwal drives but does so uppishly. Luckily for Mayank, the ball falls short of the mid off fielder.
Good length ball outside off, Agarwal guides this to gully off the back foot.
Good length ball on middle, Agarwal flicks it to the leg side. Maiden over from Abu Jayed.
Tossed up ball on middle, Jadeja defends it back to the bowler.
Floated ball on middle and leg, Ravindra flicks it to fine leg and gives Agarwal the strike.
SIX! Lovely use of the feet from Agrawal. Mehidy bowls a tossed up ball on off, Mayank dances down the track and slams this over long off for another maximum.
Mehidy tosses one up again on off, Agarwal looks for another lofted shot but does not time it well. The ball goes to long on and the batters take a single.
Flighted ball on middle, Jadeja flicks it to the leg side for nothing.
Flighted ball on off, Jadeja defends this to cover and takes a single.
Good length ball outside off, Jadeja lets the ball go to the keeper.
Good length ball on middle, Jadeja looks to flick it but gets hit on the thigh pad. The ball rolls to the off side.
Good length ball outside off, Jadeja lets the ball go to the keeper.
Jadeja defends this good length ball onto the pitch. Abu runs to collect the ball in an attempt to run Jadeja out but fails to do so. Jayed seems to have hurt his hamstring there.
Good length ball outside off, Jadeja pushes it to cover.
Good length ball on middle, Jadeja flicks it to deep square leg and picks up a couple before the fielder comes across to clean it up.
Flatter and around off, it is angled away from around the wicket. Agarwal looks to defend but it goes off the outside edge down towards third man for two.
FOUR! That is a nothing delivery! A hit-me ball. Short and down the leg side, Agarwal pulls it over square leg and gets another boundary.
Flatter and on off, gets his line this time. It is kept out.
Gives it a nice loop and lands it on middle, this is eased down to long on for one.
This is fired on the middle pole, Jadeja lunges and keeps it out.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.
On the fuller side, Agarwal opens the face of the bat and guides it through point for one.
Shorter and outside off, Jadeja cuts it towards point where the fielder dives and saves at least two for his side. Single taken.
Crisp drive! Fuller and on off, Agarwal creams it but to mid off.
Way too wide outside off, it is left alone.
A short one on middle, Agarwal evades it.
On the shorter side and on the body, this is pulled through backward square leg for one.
On the shorter side and on middle, Agarwall pulls it through mid-wicket for one. 350 up and the lead is now 200.
On middle, kept out.
On the pads, Jadeja works it to mid-wicket.

A huge appeal but not sure for what. Tha arm ball on middle, Jadeja lunges and keeps it out. the bowler is appealing as he feels it is pad first. nothing from the umpire. Replays though show that the ball did hit the pad first. However, the impact would have been umpire's call so it would have remained not out.
This is angled into the pads, Jadeja works it through mid-wicket for one.
Shorter and on middle, Agarwal pushes it through mid off for one.
FOUR! Brilliantly played from Agarwal! Hossain bowls a short of a length ball outside off, Mayank just stands tall and guides it through backward point for a boundary. Moves into the 190s now.
Good length ball on middle, Agarwal defends it back to the bowler.

Fullish delivery outside off, Agarwal was in two minds whether to leave this ball or play at it but in the end decides to shoulder arms. Sunny G on air says that this is the line that he should be bowling.
Good length ball on off, Agarwal defends it to the off side.
Short delivery on off, Agarwal rocks on his back foot  and pulls it towards deep mid-wicket and picks up a couple. Just five runs away from a wonderful double ton.
Low full toss on middle, Agarwal flicks it through mid-wicket and takes a single. 50-run stand comes up between the two.
Flatter delivery outside off, Agarwal pushes it to cover.
Full delivery on middle, Mayank works it to mid on.
Flighted delivery on middle, Agarwal pushes it to mid on.
Another flighted ball on middle, Agarwal flicks it to the leg side.

SIX! Second double century for Mayank Agarwal in Tests! This has been an innings of high class from the Karnataka opener. Since he made his debut in Australia, Mayank has grown in stature ever since. Coming to the ball, it is a flighted ball on middle, Mayank comes down the track and heaves it over deep mid-wicket for a maximum. He raises his bat and soaks in the applause from his teammates. Virat Kohli, the Indian skipper is seen signalling from the dressing room to go for the 300. Boy, Bangladesh must be ruing that dropped catch of him on Day 1.
Flighted ball on middle, Agarwal flicks it to the leg side for a single.
Outside off, it is left alone.
This is angled into the body, Agarwal works it to mid-wicket.
Fuller and on middle, Jadeja strokes it back to the bowler.
One more delivery outside off, Jadeja lets it go again.
One more ball outside off, Jadeja does not fiddle with it.
One more delivery on a length and around off, blocked.
Full toss on off, Agarwal drives it to cover for nothing.
Tosses this one on off, Mayank strides forward to defend but it takes the inside edge and the ball goes to mid-wicket. The batters take a single.
Floated ball on middle, Jadeja pushes it back to the bowler.
Flighted ball on middle, Ravindra works it to mid-wicket.
Low full toss on middle, Jadeja works it to long on and takes a single.
Flighted ball on middle, Agarwal flicks it to the leg side for a single.

FOUR! Short of a length delivery on off, Agarwal looks to pull it but gets cramped for room. He does time it well but the ball has enough to reach the deep mid-wicket fence. The fielder at deep square leg did not even attempt to stop the ball.
On a length on off, Agarwal guides this off the back foot to backward point and takes a couple.
Another one on a good length on middle, Agarwal pushes it down to mid on.
Good length ball on middle and leg, Agarwal flicks it to the leg side.
Short delivery on the leg stump line, Mayank pulls it towards fine leg and croses over for another single.
Good length ball outside off, Jadeja pushes it to cover-point and keeps strike for the next over.
Full delivery on middle and leg, Jadeja pushes it through mid on and takes the single.
Flighted ball on off, Agarwal pushes it to cover.
Flatter delivery on middle and leg, Agarwal pushes it back to the bowler.

SIX! A flat ojne this time from mayank Agarwal! Taijul tosses this one up on middle, Agarwal puts on his dancing shoes and hammers it straight down the ground for a flat maximum. Reaches his highest score in Tests.
Flighted ball on off, Agarwal defends it to cover.
Tossed up ball on off, Agarwla drives it to long off and takes a single.
Starts with a flatter delivery on off, Agarwal pushes it back to the keeper.
Floated ball outside off, Mayank lunges forward and creams this wide of long off for another couple.
FOUR! This timje finds the gap does Agarwal! Mahmudullah tosses this one up outside off, Mayank strides forward and creams the drive through extra cover for a boundary.
Defended off the back foot by the batsman.
Full delivery on middle, Agarwal drives it straight down the ground and gets to pick another couple as the fielder at long on misfields.

MISFIELD AND FOUR! This is a case of another piece of poor fielding. Flighted ball on off, Agarwal drives it to cover where the fielder misfields allowing the ball to go into the fence. The fielder from long off comes across in an attempt to stop the ball but does not reach it in time.
SIX! Jadeja loves the ball turning into him. This one though is pitched right in his zone. Full and on off, Jadeja lifts it with the angle and the turn over the mid-wicket fence. 400 up for India.
Flatter and on middle, Jadeja works it to mid-wicket.
Jadeja comes down the track but Taijul bowls it short. Jadeja pads it away.
Shorter and on middle, Jadeja pushes it to the left of the bowler who gets there quickly.
Flatter and outside off, this is pushed through covers for one.
On middle, this is kept out.
Flighted ball outside off, Jadeja defends it to cover and wants the single but is sent back.
FOUR! Easy pickings for Jadeja these! Flatter delivery down the leg side, Jadeja just helps it on its way to fine leg for a boundary.
Floated ball on middle, Jadeja flicks it to mid-wicket.
Short ball outside off, Jadeja punches this off the back foot to cover and crosses over for a single.

SIX! Stand and deliver! Mahmudullah tosses this one up on middle, Agarwal stands in his crease and lifts this over the bowler's head for another huge maximum. 100-run partnership is also up between the two.
On off, pushed towards mid on.
FOUR! Poor bowling this from Taijul. Bowls this short on pads, Jadeja pulls it to backward square leg for another boundary. Absolute mayhem from these two.
Flatter delivery on middle, Jadeja comes down the track and plays it back to the bowler.
Full delivery on middle, Jadeja flicks it towards the leg side for another single.
Loopy ball on off, Mayank pushes it towards cover and crosses over for an single.
FOUR! This is absoulte rubbish bowling from Taijul Islam! Bowls another one down the leg side. All Jadeja has to do is to get bat on it which he does. The ball goes to fine leg for another boundary.
Short of a length ball outside off, Jadeja punches this off the back foot to cover where the fielder misfields allowing the batsmen to take two.
Flighted ball on middle, Agarwla flicks it to mid-wicket.

SIX! Another one goes into the stands. Mehidy goes full outside off, Agarwal comes down the track and slams this over the long off region for another maximum. The bat came off the handle but it still has enough to go over the fence.

OUT! CAUGHT! Mayank falls after a playing a marathon of a knock. This has been a top knock from the opener and it has put India in a very commanding position. Mehidy bowls a flighted ball on middle, Agarwal plays the slog sweep towards mid-wicket but it goes straight into the hands of Abu Jayed who takes it to his right. A 300 was there for the taking but Mayank was playing for the cause of the team and perishes in doing so. A little too late for Bangladesh as this game has way beyond them to make a comeback. Just as Agarwal walks back to the pavilion, the Bangladesh players shake hands with the Karnataka batsman.
BEATEN! Flighted ball outside off, Saha looks to defend it but fails to put any bat on it.
Flatter delivery on off, Saha guides it with an angled bat towards third man and takes a couple.
The batsman defends it from within the crease.
Flatter and on middle, Jadeja works it to mid-wicket.
Flatter and on middle, Jadeja manages to keep it out again.
Jadeja comes down the track but gets too close to the pitch of the ball and ends up hitting it back to the bowler.
On middle, it is flicked to mid on.
The batsman rocks onto the back foot and punches the ball.
Misfield! Shorter and on off, this is pushed towards cover where the fielder fails to stop it and a run is taken.
SIX! That is huge! Floated ball on off, Jadeja comes down the track and heaves it over the deep mid-wicket region for a huge maximum.
Short of a length delivery outside off, Jadeja punches it to cover and takes another single.
FOUR! Saha joins the act now! Mehidy bowls a full delivery on off, Saha bends on his knees and sweeps this one through the square leg region for another boundary.
Flighted ball on off, Saha plays it to the leg side.
FOUR! Nicely played from Saha! Flatter delivery outside off, Saha plays the cut shot to third man to pick up another boundary. India's lead moves to 300 now.
Flatter delivery on middle, Saha flicks it to deep square leg and takes a single.
Good length ball on off, Saha pushes it to point and takes a single.
Back of a length ball outside off, Jadeja pushes it to cover and crosses over for another single.
Full delivery on middle, Wriddhiman flicks it to mid-wicket.
Short ball on off, Saha looks to pull it but it goes off the bottom edge to mid on.
WIDE! BOUNCER! Hossain bowls this down the leg side, Saha lets it go. The umpire gives it wide for height.

OUT! TIMBER! Finally, finally Ebadot Hossain gets his wicket of the innings. Hossain bowls this full on middle, Saha looks to flick it but hits the thigh pad and goes onto hitting the off stump. Hossain does a Cottrell like salute after picking up this wicket,
Good length ball on off, Yadav defends it to cover.
Back of a length and on off, this is pushed towards cover.
Good length again, this is pushed down to long off for one.

SIX! This is why he is out there! Yadav is out to entertain the crowd in the last few minutes of play today. Gets off the mark with a biggie. On the pads, Yadav whips it over the backward square leg fence for a biggie.
Goes for another one but this time he mistimes the pull shot over mid-wicket and two is taken.
A slower one outside off, Yadav goes after it but gets an inside edge which goes on the bounce to the keeper.
FOUR! In the gap and the dressing room is up on its feet! Full and on middle, Yadav heaves it, it goes through mid-wicket and a boundary results.
Full on middle, Jadeja flicks it to deep mid-wicket and moves to 49 with that single.

SIX! Umesh Yadav is on fire at the moment in Indore! He moves to 18 off just 6 balls. Full delivery on off, Umesh stands deep in the crease and slams this over the long on region for another maximum. The fielder looked interested for a while but it goes over his head.

SIX! Another one! This is carnage going on at the moment. Hossain bowls a short delivery down the leg side, Yadav rocks on his back foot and pulls it towards the fine leg region for a maximum. Marais Erasmus, the umpire goes upstairs to check whether it is a six or a boundary. The replays show that it is the former.
LEG BYE! Slower delivery on the pads, Yadav looks to flick it but it goes off the pads towards the leg side for a single.
The batsman defends it from within the crease.

FIFTY! 14th one for Jadeja in Tests. He has seriously improved his batting in recent times and he has shown it in this innings. Ravindra gets to the milestone by playing this length ball to the point region. He celebrates it in his traditional way, swinging his bat like a sword.
FOUR! Stand and deliver! Jadeja makes room and Jayed bowls a length ball on middle, this is smashed past mid off and a boundary results. 400 runs in the day today, 3rd time India have done so.
Direct hit and Jadeja was a goner! On the body, this is worked towards mid-wicket. They take one, Jadeja wanted a second but is sent back. The fielder throws it at the non-striker's end but misses.
Slower one outside off, this is hit down to long off for one.
TOP EDGE, FOUR! Shorter in length and on middle, Jadeja looks to pull but the ball flies off the top edge and over keeper for another boundary. Runs leaking at the moment.
Slower one on middle, Jadeja mistimes it down to long on for one.
Full and wide outside off, Yadav goes after it but misses. THAT IS STUMPS ON DAY 2!
Ishant starts with a good length ball moving away from the southpaw. Shadman keeps his eyes on the ball and leaves it alone.
Ishant comes closer to the off pole and almost finds the outside edge. It is on a length around off, in the channel of uncertainty. Shadman looks to defend but gets beaten.
Targets the stump now. It is on middle and leg, Shadman looks to defend but gets an inside edge onto the pads.
Another good movement for Ishant. It is outside off and moves away, Shadman looks to defend but gets beaten.
Back of a length on off, Shadman defends it by getting behind the line of the delivery.

Bangladesh get their scoreboard ticking. Full on off, Shadman drives it straight. He does not get it right from the meat. Shami goes after the ball and cleans it up before the ropes. The batsmen come back for the third. Shadman will keep the strike.
Starts with a good length ball on the pads, Shadman works it to fine leg and crosses over for a single.
On a length on middle with a little swing on it. Kayes works it to mid-wicket.
Good length ball on off, Kayes punches it to cover off the back foot.

FOUR! Well played that from Imrul Kayes! Gets off the mark with a boundary. Umesh bowls a half volley outside off, Kayes leans forward and creams the drive through cover for the first boundary of the game.
Fullish delivery on middle and leg, Kayes flicks it to mid-wicket.
Back of a length delivery on off, Kayes defends it to the off side.
Sharma comes around the wicket and bowls a full delivery outside off, Shadman shoulders arms to this one.
Another full delivery on middle, Islam pushes it back to the bowler.
On a length on middle and leg, Shadman  blocks it off the back foot to mid off.
Good length ball outside off, Shadman does not fiddle with it and lets the ball pass through to Saha.
Full delivery around off swinging away from the batsman. Shadman knows where his off stump is and makes a good leave.
Another full delivery outside off tempting Shadman to drive but he shoulders arms to this one.
Full delivery down the leg side, Kayes looks to flick it but misses it altogether.

Ohh! Good length ball down the leg side, Kayes looks to work it towards the leg side off the back foot. The ball brushes the thigh pad and goes to the keeper. There is an appeal for caught behind but the umpire shakes his head.
On a length on middle, Kayes works it towards square leg and takes a single.
Good length ball on middle, Islam defends it back to the bowler.
Full delivery on off, Islam attempts to defend but it goes off the outside edge and rolls to gully.
That took off from a good length area. Umesh bowls it outside off, Islam shoulders arms to this one.
BEATEN! Beautiful piece of bowling this from Sharma! Bowls a full delivery in the channel, Kayes looks to defend but it goes past the bat and into the mitts of the keeper.
Good length ball outside off, Kayes plays inside the line and lets the ball go to the keeper.
BEATEN! Another good delivery from Ishant! Full delivery outside off, Imrul looks to defend from inside the crease but fails to make any connection to it.
On a length on off coming into the batsman. Kayes looks to flick but it goes off the inside half through square leg and takes a single.
Good length ball on middle and leg, Shadman looks to work it to the leg side but goes off the leading edge to cover.
Back of a length delivery on off, Shadman defends it of the back foot to cover.

OUT! TIMBER! What a ball from Umesh to castle Imrul Kayes! This is top class stuff from the Indian pacer. Full delivery on off swinging into the batsman. Kayes looks to drive it but it goes off the inside edge and uproots the leg stump off the ground. Another early setback for the visitors.
Full delivery outside off, Mominul lets the ball go to the keeper.
FOUR! A poor ball this from Umesh! Bowls it a bit too full and wide outside off, Mominul prods forward and drives it through point for a boundary. Gets off the mark with that.
Good length ball outside off, Mominul shoulders arms to this one.

NOT OUT! Poor review this from India! It is not going above the stumps but it is certainly missing the off stump. Good length ball outside off swinging into the batsman, Mominul decides to leave it but the ball brushes his pad and gos to the keeper. Yadav appeals for a LBW but the umpire shakes his head. Yadav is convinced that it is out and forces Kohli to go for the review. The Ultra Edge then rolls in and it shows no bat. The Ball Tracker shows that the ball was going on to miss the off stump. India have lost their first review here courtesy of a poor decision from the Indian skipper.
Another good length ball outside off swinging into the batsman, Haque lets the ball go to the keeper.
Good length ball shaping away from outside off, Shadman leaves it alone.
Full on middle and leg, Shadman flicks it through mid-wicket and gets a couple.
Full and coming in on off, Shadman keeps his eyes on the ball and defends right unedr his eye line.

In the air and taken...but it came off the pads. Good length ball that comes in. Shadman looks to flick but misses. The ball lobs to gully off the pads and Jadeja takes it. There is a stifled appeal but it is turned down as the ball came off the pads. Harsha Bhogle on air, gets excited thinking it came off the bat but it wasn't.
Fuller on the stumps, Islam defends it off the front foot.

OUT! Bowled! Right through the gate of bat and pad. A fast bowler's delight. India dominating. This is brilliant bowling from Ishant. Length ball pitching on off, Ishant makes the ball jag back in. Shadman looks to push it straight but the ball sneaks right through his bat and pad and goes onto hit middle and leg. This Indian side is lethal with the cherry in the hand and today has not been any different so far. Bangladesh two down and the trail is a massive 327.
Full delivery on off swinging into the batsman. Mominul looks to flick but it goes off the inside half of the bat through square leg. The batters take a couple.
Umesh dishes out another full delivery on off, Haque looks to work it to the leg side again. The ball takes the inside edge of the bat and rolls to square leg.
Full delivery on off, Mominul pushes it to mid off.
Fullish in length in the channel outside off, Haque lets the ball go to the keeper.
Good length ball way outside off, Mominul lets the ball go to the keeper.
Back of a length delivery outside off, Mominul shoulders arms to this one.
Short of a length delivery on off, Mithun keeps his bat down and lets the ball go to the keeper.
Full delivery outside off, Mithun does not fiddle with it and shoulders arms to this one.
Good length ball on middle, Mithun defends it back to the bowler.
Full delivery outside off, Mithun again leaves the ball alone.

Good length ball on off swinging in a mile. Mithun looks to defend it but misses it to get wrapped on the pads. Ishant and his teammates appeal for an LBW but nothing from the umpire. They have a long chat about the review but decide against it. Good decision as the Ball Tracker shows that it is going over the stumps.
Good length ball on off, Mithun looks to defend it but it goes off the inside edge of the bat onto the pads. No run.
Full delivery on off moving into the batsman, Mominul looks to drive but it hits the inside half of the bat and rolls to square leg for a single.
Full delivery down the leg side, Mohammad attempts the flick shot but misses it.
BEATEN! Beautifully bowled! Yadav bowls it outside off swinging away a bit. Mithun looks to defend it but the ball goes past the outside edge and into the keeper's gloves.
Full delivery on middle, Mithun works it to square leg and picks up a single.

Good length ball on middle, Mominul looks to defend but it hits him on the thigh pad. Umesh appeals but the umpire shakes his head. It probably was going over the stumps. Kohli signals not to take the review as it was going over.

BEATEN! Excellent bowling this from Umesh. He bowls it short of a length on off, Mominul looks to uncomfortably fend at it but the ball goes to the keeper. Yadav appeals for a caught behind but nothing from the umpire.
Full delivery on middle, Mithun drives it to mid on for nothing.
FOUR! Nicely played! Short ball outside off, Mithun camps on his back foot and plays the square cut through third man for a boundary.
Good length ball down the leg side, Mithun attempts to flick it but misses it completely.
Full delivery on middle, Mithun drives it straight but Ishant gets a hand on it and the ball rolls it to mid on. No run.
Good length ball on off, Mithun defends it to cover and picks up a single.
Good length ball outside off, Mominul plays inside the line and leaves the ball alone.

FOUR! Terrific shot! Full delivery outside off, Mithun leans into the drive and plays it through the cover region for a boundary. The fielder from cover tries to chase after it but the ball wins the race.
EDGED AND FOUR! Lucky for Mithun here! Good length ball on off, Mithun looks to defend it but the ball goes off the outside edge past gully and into the fence.
Full delivery on middle, Mithun defends it to mid on.
Short of a length delivery outside off, Mohammad sways away from it and lets the ball go to the keeper.
On a length on middle and leg, Mithun looks to flick but it hits the pads and rolls back to the bowler.
OHH! Good length ball around off swinging in a little, Mithun lets the ball go to the keeper. The ball goes just past the off stump. Good leave in the end.
Starts with a short of a length ball outside off, Mominul sways away from it.
FOUR LEG BYES! Good length ball on the pads, Haque looks to flick but the ball brushes the thigh pad and races to the fine leg fence.
Shami comes around the wicket and bowls a good length ball outside off, Mominul shoulders arms to this one.
On a length outside off, Haque does not fiddle with it and lets the ball go to the keeper.

OUT! LBW! Excellent review from Shami and India! One review was wasted and they have made full use of the second. Good length ball on middle and leg, Mominul moves towards the off side and looks to flick it. Shami puts in a huge appeal but the umpire shakes his head. He convinces Kohli to go for the review and the skipper obliges. The Ball Tracker rolls in and it is showing all reds. The ball was going on to hit the leg stump. Bangladesh three down now and are in need of something special now.
Good length ball on middle, Rahim looks to flick it but gets it off the inside edge and rolls towards square leg for a single. Gets off the mark with that single.

Full ball shaping in. It looks to be going down leg, Mushfiqur looks to flick but the ball goes off his pad to the on side. There is a stifled appeal but Umesh does not go up initially. He later does and the umpire is unmoved. They steal a leg bye.
FOUR! Slightly overpitched and Mithun makes the most of it. It is on middle and leg, Mithun flicks it through mid-wicket for a boundary.
Good length ball outside off, Mithun leaves it alone.

NOT OUT! Bad review this from the hosts. They have lost both their reviews here. Length ball pitching on middle and leg, Mithun looks to drive but misses. The ball hits him on the pads. The Indian players go up in a confident appeal but the umpire is unmoved. The Indian players are sure they have their man and skipper, Virat Kohli takes it upstairs. Replay rolls in and it shows there is no bat. Ball Tracker then rolls in and it shows that the ball was going onto miss the leg pole.
Good length ball outside off, Mithun looks to defend but misses.
On the pads, Mithun looks to flick but the ball goes off the pads and they take a leg bye.

OUT! CAUGHT! Brilliant bowling this from Shami! Short of a length ball on middle, Mithun gets hurried onto his pull and the ball goes off the upper half of his towards Agarwal at short mid-wicket. He settles under it and takes a simple catch. Bangladesh falling like nine pins here in Indore. The Bangla Tigers are surrendering here without a fight.
Good length ball on off, Mahmudullah defends it to point.
Full delivery on off, Mahmudullah looks to defend it but it hits the inside edge onto the pads. No run.
Good length ball outside off, Mahmudullah shoulders arms to this one.
On a length on middle, Mahmudullah defends it back to the bowler.
BEATEN! Excellent bowling this. Full delivery outside off, Mahmudullah gets tempted into playing the drive but the ball goes past the bat and into the mitts of the keeper.
Full delivery outside off, Mushfiqur lets the ball go to the keeper.
Good length ball around off, Mushfiqur shoulders arms to this one.
Another good length ball outside off, Rahim does not fiddle with it and lets it go to the keeper.
Good length ball on off, Rahim guides it through the gully region and takes three. Agarwal hares after it from gully and makes a good sliding stop. Saves a run for his side.
Full delivery on middle, Mahmudullah drives it uppishly but luckily for him, the ball goes to mid off on the bounce.
BOUNCER! It is bowled way over the head of Mahmudullah who ducks under it. It is given as a wide by the umpire.
On a length outside off, Mahmudullah lets the ball go to Saha.

DROPPED! Rohit Sharma drops a sitter! Mushfiqur Rahim was dropped twice in the first innings as well and the trend has continued in the second innings as well. Fullish delivery outside off, Rahim attempts to drive but it goes off the outside edge of the bat to Rohit at second slip who makes a complete mess of it. Shami looks distraught.
Good length ball outside off, Rahim shoulders arms to this one.
On a length on middle, Rahim defends it off the front foot.
Full delivery outside off swinging away, Rahim shoulders arms to this one.
BEATEN! Another piece of excellence from Shami! Bowls it on a length outside off, Rahim attempts to poke at it but the ball goes past the outside edge of the bat and into the gloves of the keeper.
Good length ball on middle, Rahim defends it to the leg side. Excellent over from Shami comes to an end. Could have taken a wicket too but it was not to be.
Good length ball outside off, Mahmudullah leaves it alone.
Length ball outside off, Mahmudullah shoulders arms to it.
Full around off, Mahmudullah looks to defend but it goes off the outer half towards gully.
This one comes in. It is on a length on off, Mahmudullah reads it well and defends it.
Good length ball way outside off, it swings away. Mahmudullah is in no mood to have a go at that.
Fuller outside off, Mahmudullah lunges forward and lets the ball carry to the keeper.
Very full on middle and leg, almost a yorker. Rahim does well to glance it towards wide mid on for a single.
Full outside off, Mahmudullah squeezes it to the right of point. The fielder there dives but misfields allowing them to take a single. That also takes Bangladesh's total to 50.
Good length ball on off, Mushfiqur plays it to point for a run.
Back of a length ball outside off, Mushfiqur leaves it alone. Shami generates good bounce as it goes to the keeper around his head.
FOUR! A rare bad ball from Shami. He bowls it full on the pads, Mahmudullah flicks it fine down the leg side for a boundary.
Beauty to finish. Good length ball outside off, it shapes away just a bit. Mahmudullah looks to defend but gets squared up.
Good length ball on middle and leg, it zips in. Mushfiqur looks to defend but misses and gets hit high on the thigh pad.
Fuller on middle and leg, this too comes in. Mushfiqur looks to flick but gets an inside edge onto the pads.
Another zipper. It is on middle, Rahim manages to flick it behind square on the leg side for a single.

Direct hit and Mushfiqur would have been in a world of trouble here. Full and swinging in on off, Mahmudullah defends it with soft hands towards cover and calls for a quick single. Rahim was a bit hesitant but goes through with it. Umesh Yadav runs in and gets to the ball quickly. He has a shy at the keeper's end but misses.
Full and another good inswinger. Rahim looks to defend but gets an inside edge onto the pads. The ball goes to the off side and they take a quick single and this time with ease.
Fuller on off, Mahmudullah defends it off the front foot.
Fuller outside off, Rahim knows where his off stump is and leaves it alone.
Length ball outside off, Mushfiqur looks to punch it on the off side but misses. The ball just about misses the edge.
Outside off, Rahim leaves it alone.
On the pads, Mushi looks to flick but the ball goes off his pad and they take a leg bye.
Fuller on off, Mahmudullah defends it off the front foot.
Oh close! Full and swinging in, Mahmudullah looks to defend but luckily gets an inside edge onto the pads.
Full on middle and leg, Rahim flicks it to mid-wicket.
Good length ball outside off, the ball shapes away. Rahim looks to defend but gets beaten.
Back of a length ball on off, Rahim defends it off the back foot.
Full on off and middle, Rahim defends it towards cover and shouts a loud no to his partner.

Direct hit and this would have been close. Good length ball on off, Rahim nudges it to cover-point and calls for a quick single. Jadeja gets to the ball and has a shy at the keeper's end but misses. Had he hit, Mahmudullah could have been in trouble.
Length ball outside off, Mahmudullah leaves it alone. That will be Lunch on Day 3.

No ball and a leg bye. Shami starts with a no ball.  He oversteps the line and delivers a length ball on the pads. Rahim looks to flick but the ball goes off his pad to the on side and they steal a leg bye.

Edged but well short. Good length ball shaping away. Mahmudullah looks to defend it with soft hands but it goes off the outside edge towards third slip. The ball falls short to the right of Kohli. He tries to stop it but fails to stop it and they take a run.
Outside off on a length, Mushifiqur leaves it alone.
Another ball outside off, Rahim has nothing to do with it.
Back of a length ball on off, Mushfiqur gets on his back foot and blocks it.
Length ball around off, Mushfiqur looks to defend but it goes off the outer half of his bat towards point.
On top of off pole, Rahim dabs it towards point.
Jadeja starts with a floated delivery on middle and leg, Mahmudullah glances it to the on side.
Tossed up on off, Mahmudullah defends it with calmness.
Tossed up on middle, Mahmudullah looks to defend but the ball goes off the inner half of his bat towards square leg for a single.
Flighted on off, Rahim looks to defend but does so off the outside half of his bat.
Floated on middle, Rahim flicks it on the bounce to the right of short leg.
Slightly quicker from Jadeja. It is outside off, Mushfiqur looks to sweep but misses.
Fuller on off, Mahmudullah strokes it through point for a single as the fielder cleans it up with a slide.
Good length ball on off, Mushfiqur defends it off the front foot.
Back of a length ball on off, Mushfiqur defends it towards point.
Fuller on middle and off, Rahim defends it off the front foot.
No swing on this one. It is outside off, Rahim does not go chasing after it.
Beautiful delivery! Shami steams in and bowls a fuller ball outside off, it is in the channel of uncertainty. The ball swings away, Rahim looks to defend but gets beaten.
Floated on middle, Mahmudullah defends it off the front foot.

FOUR! Bad ball and Mahmudullah is quick to lash onto it. Short and wide outside off, Mahmudullah cuts it through point. Kohli at backward point dives and gets his fingers to it but cannot stop it and the ball races to the fence.
Floated on off, Mahmudullah defends it.
Flighted on off, Mahmudullah drives it through covers for a couple.
Tossed up on middle and off, Mahmudullah drives it to the man at cover.
Shorter on off, Mahmudullah defends it onto the ground.
On the pads, Mushfiqur looks to flick but the ball goes off his pads to the on side for a leg bye.
Fuller on off, Mahmudullah drives it to the right of mid off. Jadeja dives to his right and saves runs for his side. India have a lot of runs to play with but they are fighting for all of it.

OUT! Caught! Rohit Sharma has finally taken the catch here. Shami is a happy man. Third wicket for the second innings specialist. Good length ball on off, it zips away. Mahmudullah has a poke at it but gets a thick outside edge towards second slip. Rohit Sharma there makes no mistake this time and takes a good catch to his right. Half the side back in the hut. Credit has to go to Jadeja as well as he saved runs in the previous ball which might have added a bit of anxiousness in the batsman. They trail by another massive 271 runs.
Outside off, Liton starts his innings with a solid leave.
Fuller on off, Liton pushes it back to the bowler.

FOUR! Liton is off the mark in style. He looked promising in the first innings and he has started off well here too. Fuller on off, slightly overpitched. Das leans into the drive and creams it through covers for a boundary.
Flatter on off, Rahim defends it.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.
FOUR! Mushfiqur is a very good player of spin and this is a proof of it. Floated on off, Rahim gets on his knee and slog sweeps it over mid-wicket for a boundary.
FOUR! This time through the off side. Jadeja goes short so Rahim goes on his back foot and slashes it through point for a boundary.
Quicker on middle and leg, Rahim looks to defend but it goes fine down the leg side off the inner half of his bat for a single.
Tossed up on off, Liton looks to defend but gets an outside edge which goes to point.
Back of a length ball outside off, Rahim lets it carry to the keeper.
Outside off, Mushfiqur leaves it alone.
Way outside off, Mushi does not disturb that.
Around the pads, MR flicks it to mid-wicket.
Full and swinging away. Rahim pushes it to mid on.
Good length ball outside off, Mushfiqur leaves it alone.
Shorter on middle, Das punches it to mid on and gets to the other end.
Floated on off, Rahim punches it to mid off for a single.
Floated on off, Das pushes it to cover for a single.
Tossed up on off, Rahim keeps it out.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat
Shorter on off, Rahim pushes it to point.
FOUR! Plays it with soft hand. Back of a length ball on off, Das opens the face of the bat and just uses the pace of the bowler to send it wide of gully for a boundary.

FOUR! Gorgeous shot! Slightly overpitched on middle and leg, Liton gets on his front foot and plays the on side to perfection for a boundary. The fielder gave it a chase but had no chance stopping that.
Typical fast bowler's response. After being hit for a boundary on the previous delivery. Ishant bangs it in short. Das ducks under it.
Outside off, Das leaves it alone.
Pacy ball on off, Das looks to defend but gets an inside edge onto the pads.
FOUR! The over ends the way it started, with a boundary. Full outside off, Liton leans into his drive and creams it through covers for a boundary. 100 comes up for Bangladesh with that shot.
Flighted ball on middle, Rahim flicks it to mid-wicket and takes a single.

BEATEN! Excellent delivery! Floated ball around off spinning away, Das looks to defend it but it goes past the bat to the keeper. Jadeja puts in a huge appeal but the umpire shakes his head. India have no reviews left so they cannot go upstairs.
Short delivery on off, Das punches it off the back foot to point.
Punched off the back foot by the batsman.
Full delivery on middle, Das defends it back to the bowler.
FOUR! Nicely played! Short ball on middle, Das works it to the deep mid-wicket region and picks up another boundary.
On the pads, Mushfiqur looks to flick but misses and gets hit on the pads.
Down the leg side, Rahim looks to flick but misses.
Fuller on off, Mushfiqur flicks it but it goes off the inner half of his bat for a single.
Short ball on middle, Liton looks to pull it but it goes off the top half of the bat towards mid-wicket. Pujara jumps up to catch it but it goes over his head. The batters take a couple.
Good length ball on off, Das pushes it to covers and takes a quick single.
On a length on middle, Rahim defends it back to the bowler.
Flatter delivery on middle, Das works it to the leg side and picks up a single.
FOUR! Some innovation shown by Rahim! Ashwin bowls a flighted ball on off, Mushfiqur bends on his knees and plays a reverse sweep through third man for a boundary.
Flatter delivery on off, Rahim defends it off the front foot and into the pitch. The ball goes just past the off stump and into the keeper's gloves.
BEATEN! Flighted ball outside off, Rahim looks to cut it but fails to put any bat on it.
Short ball on middle, Rahim pulls it through square leg and takes off for a single.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.
Flighted ball on middle, Rahim defends it off the front foot.
FOUR! Well played! Short ball outside off, Rahim rocks on his back foot and punches it through covers for a boundary.
Flatter delivery outside off, Rahim punches it to cover and takes a single.
Floated ball outside off, Das lets the ball go to the keeper.
Flighted ball outside off, Das defedns it to the off side and takes off for a quick run. The fielder has a shy at the keeper's end but misses it.
FOUR! Floated ball on middle, Rahim plays another sweep shot towards deep square leg and picks up another boundary.
FOUR! Beautifully played! Full delivery outside off, Das leans forward and drives it through mid off for another boundary. This is excellent batting from these two.
Flighted ball outside off, Das guides it through third man and takes a couple before the fielder can cut it off.
Flighted ball on middle, Das works it to the leg side.
Flatter delivery on off, Das defends it off the back foot.
Another flat delivery on middle, Liton defends it to the bowler.
Loopy delivery on off, Das blocks it out.
Flatter delivery outside off, Rahim blocks it to point.
Full delivery on middle, Rahim plays it back to the bowler.
Floated ball outside off, Rahim lunges forward and pushes it to cover.
Quicker delivery on off, Mushfiqur rocks on his back foot and defends it to the off side.
Flighted ball outside off, Rahim defends it to the off side.

BYES! Jadeja bowls it slower through the air which spins away, Rahim looks to drive it but misses it. Saha fails to collect it cleanly and the ball goes past Rahane at first slip to third man. The batters steal 2 leg byes. The replays show that Rahim has made his way out of the crease so it was a stumping gone wrong.
Flighted ball on off, Das pushes it to cover.
Full delivery on middle, Das pushes it back to the bowler.
Loopy ball on middle, Das works it to mid on and takes a single.
Flatter delivery on middle, Rahim defends it off the back foot.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.
Flat delivery on off, Rahim pushes it to point.
Full delivery on middle, Das defends it back to the bowler.
Floated ball on middle, Das punches it back to the bowler.
On off, defended off the back foot to point.
Full delivery on middle, Liton defends it back to the bowler.
Loopy delivery outside off, Das pushes it to cover and takes a single.
BEATEN! Flatter delivery outside off, Rahim looks to defend it of the back foot but the ball goes past the outside edge and into the mitts of the keeper.
Floated ball on off, Das defends it to the off side.

OUT! CAUGHT! Ashwin gets his first wicket of this innings. Bowls a flighted ball on middle, Das comes down the wicket and looks to play it over the bowler;s head. He does not time it well and Ashwin puts his hands to his right and pouches it safely. A budding partnership is broken. India would look to finish things off quickly now.
Loopy ball on off spinning into the batsman, Hasan looks to defend it but it goes off the gloves towards square leg. Suddenly, the things have started to happen off the pitch.
The batsman shows the full face of the bat and defends the ball off the back foot.
BEATEN! Loopy ball outside off, Hasan looks to defend it but misses the ball completely.
Loopy ball on middle, Hasan comes down the track and pushes it straight back going onto hitting the stumps at the bowler's end.
Full delivery on middle, Rahim defends it back to the bowler.
Short delivery outside off, Rahim guides it to third man for nothing.
Flatter delivery on middle, Rahim defends it back to the bowler.
Quicker delivery on off, Rahim gets his bat down in time and pushes it to cover.
Flatter delivery on middle and leg, Rahim flicks it to square leg and takes a single.
Loopy ball on middle, Mehidy blocks it out.
Flatter delivery on off, Mushfiqur defends it off the back foot.
Flatter delivery outside off, Rahim pushes it from the back foot to cover and takes a single.
Flat delivery outside off, Hasan defends it off the back foot.
Loopy ball outside off, Das lunges forward and defends it to point.
SIX! Hasan gets off the pair with a lovely use of the feet. Flighted ball on off, Mehidy dabnces down the track and heaves it straight over the bowler's head for a maximum.
Floated ball on middle, Hasan plays it to mid on and takes a single.
BEATEN! Beautifully bowled! Floats this one up outside off, Hasan lunges forward to defend it but misses it altogether.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
Flighted ball on middle, Hasan defends it to the leg side.
Flatter delivery on middle and leg, Hasan works it to mid-wicket for nothing.
Another flat delivery on middle, worked towards the leg side.
Full delivery outside off, Mehidy pushes it to long off and picks up a single.
Flatter delivery outside off, Mehidy looks to defend it but it goes off the outside edge of the bat through third man. Pujara runs after it to clean it up but not before the batters take a couple.
Full delivery on middle, Hasan works it to long on and takes a single.
Flighted ball outside off, Rahim pushes it through covers for a two.
Floated ball on off, Rahim pushes it to covers and takes a single.
FOUR! Nicely played! Short of a length delivery outside off, Hasan rocks on his back foot and punches it towards the backward point region for a boundary.
On off, defended it to the off side.
Flighted ball on middle, Rahim defends it back to the bowler.
FOUR! Poor bowling this from Jadeja! Short of a length ball outside off, Rahim cuts it off the back foot and past the diving fielder and into the fence.
Flatter delivery on middle, Rahim works it to the leg side for a couple.
Full on off, played to cover for a single.
Full delivery on middle, Hasan defends it back to the bowler.
Full delivery on middle, Hasan blocks it out.

Just over! Quicker off spinner. It is boiwled at around 95 kph. It is just outside off, Rahim initially looks to play but then decides to leave. Too late as the ball hits the handle of the bat and lobs over Ajinkya Rahane at first slip. They take a run.
Floated on the pads, Mehidy flicks it to mid-wicket.
Tossed up on off, Hasan defends it.
Flighted on off, Mehidy pushes it to cover.
On the stumps, kept out by Mehidy.

FOUR! Excellent use of the feet. Flighted on off, Mehidy comes down the trakc and loft it over cow corner. Shami runs to his right from long on and it looks to be half a chance but the ball falls short and goes away to the fence.
Full delivery on middle, Rahim defends it off the front foot back to the bowler.
Full delivery outside off, Rahim pushes it to cover for nothing.
Full delivery on middle and leg, Rahim works it to the leg side.
Flighted ball on off, Mushfiqur blocks it out.
BEATEN! Nicely bowled! Flighted ball outside off, Rahim looks to defend it but misses it completely.
On off, defended it off the front foot.
Tosses this one up on off, Hasan pushes it back to the bowler.
Flighted ball outside off landing on the rough. The ball spins a mile into the batsman. Mehidy lets the ball go to the keeper. The ball just passes the off stump by a whisker.
BEATEN! Flighted ball outside off, Hasan looks to defend it but fails to make any connection to it.
On middle, Hasan flicks it to mid-wicket.
The batsman shows the full face of the bat and defends the ball off the back foot.
Flatter delivery on middle, Hasan defends it back to the bowler off the back mfoot.

FIFTY! 20TH Fifty for Rahim in Tests. Full delivery on middle, Rahim flicks it to the deep square leg region and takes a couple to reach the landmark. It has been a good innings from him so far and has held the innings together. Not much of a celebration from him as he knows that there is still a long way to go.
Good length ball outside off, Rahim lets it go to the keeper.
Outside off, left alone by Rahim.
On a length outside off, Rahim initially looks to defend but chooses to leave the ball at the last moment.
Fullish delivery on the pads, Mushfiqur flicks it to deep square leg and crosses over for a single.
Full delivery on middle, Hasan defends it back to the bowler.
Flighted ball on off, Rahim plays the paddle sweep towards fine leg and takes a single.
Floated ball on off, Mehidy defends it to cover.
Full delivery on off, Hasan works it to long on and takes a single.
BEATEN! Beautifully played! Flighted ball outside off, Rahim rocks on his back foot and looks to cut it but fails to get anything on it.
Floated ball on off, Rahim dances down the tack and defends it to cover.
Full delivery on middle, Rahim flicks it to mid-wicket.
Full delivery on middle, Hasan flicks it to the backward square leg region for a couple. Mayank runs across from deep square leg and cuts it off.
EDGED AND FOUR! Back of a length ball outside off, Hasan looks to cut it but it goes off the outside edge over Rohit's head at second slip. The ball rolls to the third man fence.
Good length ball on off, Hasan defends it to cover.
Full delivery on off, Hasan pushes it to mid off.
BOUNCER! It is bowled over Hasan's head. Hasan ducks under it.
Back of a length delivery on middle, Hasan flicks it to deep square leg and keeps strike for the next over.
Good length ball outside off, Hasan looks to push it towards the off side but the ball sneaks under the bat and into the keeper's gloves.
Good length ball on off, Hasan defends it to cover.
On a length on middle, Hasan flicks it to mid-wicket.
FOUR! Thrashed! Good length ball outside off, Mehidy stands tall and drives it through cover to pick up another boundary.
BOUNCER! A well directed one at that. Hasan ducks under it.
On a length on middle, Hasan plays it back to the bowler.
Good length ball on off, Rahim looks to defend it but it hits the inside edge going onto hitting the pads. No run.
Full delivery on off, Rahim pushes it to mid off.
On a length outside off, Mushfiqur lets the ball go to the keeper.
Back of a length delivery outside off, Rahim shoulders arms to this one.
Good length ball on middle, Rahim flicks it towards deep square leg and gives Hasan the strike.
Full delivery on the pads, Hasan flicks it to mid on and takes a single. 50-run stand is up between the two.
Good length ball on off, Mehidy blocks it out.
Back of a length delivery on middle, Hasan works it to mid-wicket.
Full delivery on middle and leg, Hasan works it through mid-wicket and picks up a boundary. The fielders from mid on and mid-wicket hare after it but fail to stop the ball.
Full delivery on middle, Hasan pushes it to mid on.
Fullish delivery outside off, Hasan plays a nice looking drive but finds the cover fielder. No run.

Good length ball on off, Hasan looks to defend it but it goes off the outside edge to third man for a couple. Pujara at gully is late to react and forces Ishant from point to clean it up. TEA ON DAY 3.
Starts with a full delivery on middle, Rahim pushes it back to the bowler. It deflects off his hand and the ball rolls to mid on.
Good length ball on middle and leg, Rahim flicks it through square leg and picks up a couple before Mayank can clean it up.
Short ball at middle stump, Rahim ducks under it.
On a length on the pads, Rahim flicks it to fine leg and takes a single.

OUT! Bowled! That was a stunning delivery from Umesh! It has come in viciously. Slightly shorter around off, the ball jags back in. Mehidy looks to play at it but then decides to leave. He is caught in between the two. The ball hits his elbow, then his body and then it goes onto hit the stumps. This partnership was starting to become the buzzing bee around Indian ears but Mehdiy has to walk back. He cannot wrap around his head with what has happened here. He is reluctant to leave but then walks back. Wicket off the first over of the session. Mehidy holds his elbow as he walks back. India are all smiles and joy at the moment.
Good length ball outside off, Taijul leaves it alone.
Flighted ball on the pads, Rahim flicks it to fine leg and takes a single.
Full delivery on middle, Taijul defends it to the leg side.
Fullish delivery on middle, Taijul defends it back to the bowler.
Tossed up ball outside off, Taijul pushes it to covers and takes a single.
Flighted ball on off, Mushfiqur defends it off the front foot to cover.
On off, blocked to cover by Rahim.
Good length ball outside off, Taijul lets the ball go to the keeper.
Fullish delivery outside off, Taijul shoulders arms to this one.
Comes around the wicket does Umesh and bowls a full delivery in the channel outside off, Islam does not fiddle with it and lets the ball go to the keeper.
Back of a length delivery onoff, Taijul rocks on his back foot and defends it to cover.
Full delivery outside off, Taijul shoulders arms to this time.
BEATEN! Nicely bowled! Full delivery outside off, Taijul looks to defend but the ball goes past the outside edge and the keeper collects it cleanly.
Tossed up ball on middle, Rahim works it to the leg side and takes a single.
Full delivery on off, Taijul plays it back to the bowler.
Flatter delivery on middle, Taijul blocks it out.
Full delivery outside off, Islam pushes it to cover for nothing.
Tossed up ball on off, Taijul looks to drive it but it goes off the inside half towards square leg. No run.
Full delivery on middle, Taijul flicks it to mid-wicket.
Good length ball on off, Rahim camps on the back foot and defends it to the off side.
Good length ball on middle, Rahim pushes it to cover-point and calls Taijul for a quick single.

Another gem from Umesh! That was not far away from sending Taijul back. Good length ball around off, Taijul looks to defend it but it goes off the thigh pad towards Saha. He dives to his left but fails to collect it cleanly. The Indians appeal for LBW but the umpire shakes his head. Very good decision from the umpire as the Ball Tracker rolls in later on and it shows that the ball was missing the stumps. Good decision from the umpire.
FOUR! Good length ball outside off, Islam looks to defend it but it goes off the outside edge to third man for a boundary.
Good length ball outside off, Islam punches it to the off side and takes a single.
Full delivery on off, Rahim defends it off the front foot.
Full delivery on middle, Taijul flicks it the leg side.
Flighted ball on middle, Taijul blocks it onto the pitch.
Tossed up ball on middle, Taijul defends it back to the bowler.
Flighted ball on off, Islam looks to defend it but it goes off the inside edge onto the pads. Ashwin appeals but the umpire is unmoved.
Tossed up ball on off, Taijul attempts to defend it yet again but gets an inside edge onto the pads. Ashwin appeals yet again but the replays show that there was bat on it.
Flatter delivery outside off, Islam attempts to defend it but fails to make a connection.
On a length on off, Rahim defends it onto the pitch.
Good length ball on middle, Rahim defends it back to the bowler.
On a length outside off, Rahim lets the ball go to the keeper.
Short ball outside off, Mushfiqur sways away from it.
Good length ball around off, Rahim lets the ball go to the keeper.
On a length outside off, Rahim again lets the ball go to the keeper. Maiden over from Shami.
Full delivery on off, Taijul defends it back to Ashwin.
Flatter delivery outside off, Islam lunges forward and defends it to point.
Full delivery on middle, Islam defends it out.
Flighted ball on off, blocks it out.

On middle, defended it out.
BOUNCER! It is bowled above the head of the batsman who ducks under it.
Full delivery outside off, Rahim shoulders arms to this one.
Good length ball on off, Rahim looks to defend but it goes off the outside edge towards the slip cordon. The fielder there collects it on the bounce.
Yorker around off, Rahim digs it out to the bowler.
Good length ball on off, Rahim guides it to gully.
Full delivery outside off, Rahim defends it to cover. Fourth maiden in a row.
Full delivery on middle, Taijul plays it back to Ashwin.

OHH! What happened there? Flighted ball outside off, Taijul looks to defend it but the ball goes off the pads towards second slip. Ashwin and the rest appeal but nothing from the umpire. It looks very close to the naked eye. The Ultra Edge is shown later and there is a spike on it. Harsha Bhogle on air says that save the reviews for later nad that is proved right here.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.
Full delivery on middle, Islam defends it out.
BEATEN! Flighted ball outside off, Islam looks for the drive but fails to make any connection to it.
On middle, flicked to mid-wicket.
Full on off and middle, Mushfiqur defends it off the front foot.
Length ball on off, Mushfiqur strokes it through point for a single.
The batsman shows the full face of the bat and defends the ball off the back foot.
Bouncer! Islam ducks under it.
Good length ball on off, Taijul tucks it to mid-wicket.
Length ball outside off, Islam looks to defend inside the line and the ball goes to the keeper.
FOUR! Nicely played from Rahim! Flatter delivery outside off, Rahim plays the late cut to third man for a boundary. Ishant runs after it from third man but gives up the chase.
Flighted ball on middle, Rahim comes down the track and plays it back to the bowler.
On middle, Rahim blocks it to the leg side.
Floated ball on middle, Mushfiqur defends it to the leg side.
The batsman flicks it away with a wristy shot.
On middle, Rahim blocks it out to the leg side.
BEATEN! Good length ball outside off, Taijul pokes at it but fails to put any bat on it.
Full delivery on middle, Taijul plays it back to the bowler.

OUT! CAUGHT! Shami gets his fourth wicket of the innings and continues his tradition of being amazing in the second innings. The short ball does the trick for the hosts. Shami bowls it aimed at the body, Taijul looks to fend it uncomfortably but it hits the upper half of the bat and goes up in the air. Saha moves a liitle forward and takes a simple catch. India just two wickets away from a massive victory here.
Back of a length delivery outside off, Abu Jayed looks to guide it to the off side but fails to put any bat on it.

DROPPED! Jadeja drops a tough catch at gully. Full delivery on middle, Jayed makes room for himself towards the leg side and looks to poke at it. It goes off the outside edge towards Ravindra Jadeja at gully. He goes at it with one hand but does not hold onto it.
Good length ball outside off, Jayed lets the ball go to the keeper.
Flatter delivery on off spinning into the batsman, Mushfiqur blocks it out.
Full delivery on middle, Rahim flicks it to deep mid-wicket and refuses the single.
Flatter delivery on middle, Rahim works it to the leg side.
Short delivery on middle, Rahim plays it back to the bowler.

OUT! CAUGHT! Rahim after showing a lot of patience perishes in trying to clear the boundary. Ashwin bowls a flighted delivery on off, Mushfiqur looks to play the slog sweep but the bat turns in his hand. The ball goes towards long off and Pujara runs behind from mid off and takes a good running catch. Just one wicket away are the hosts.
Full delivery on off, Jayed defends it to the off side.
Good length ball on middle, Hossain flicks it towards the leg side and takes a single.
FOUR! Beautiful shot! Full delivery on middle, Jayed plays a straight drive through mid on and picks up the boundary.
Good length ball down the leg side, Abu Jayed lets the ball go to the keeper in an uncomfortable manner.
Full delivery on of, Jayed defends it towards cover.
Short of a length delivery on middle, Jayed looks to play the upper cut but misses it completely.
BEATEN! That is a wild slog from Jayed! Shami bowls this full outside off, Abu goes for a heave over long on but fails to make any connection to it.
Flighted ball on middle, Hossain defends it out.

OUT! CAUGHT! That is the end of that! Umesh Yadav takes a terrific catch at long on to complete the formalities. Ashwin bowls a floated ball on off, Hossain looks for a wild slog over long on but it goes off the splice of the bat. Umesh Yadav runs across from the deep and takes a good catch tumbling to his left. With that, INDIA WIN BY AN INNINGS AN 130 RUNS.
